		<img alt='' src='https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/39ae42d33af99a13fa6ef7e7c81e595cc0e2e241e360bb495dc7e4c89ab517fd?s=42&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' srcset='https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/39ae42d33af99a13fa6ef7e7c81e595cc0e2e241e360bb495dc7e4c89ab517fd?s=42&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G 1x, https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/39ae42d33af99a13fa6ef7e7c81e595cc0e2e241e360bb495dc7e4c89ab517fd?s=63&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G 1.5x, https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/39ae42d33af99a13fa6ef7e7c81e595cc0e2e241e360bb495dc7e4c89ab517fd?s=84&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G 2x, https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/39ae42d33af99a13fa6ef7e7c81e595cc0e2e241e360bb495dc7e4c89ab517fd?s=126&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G 3x, https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/39ae42d33af99a13fa6ef7e7c81e595cc0e2e241e360bb495dc7e4c89ab517fd?s=168&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G 4x' class='avatar avatar-42' height='42' width='42' loading='lazy' decoding='async' />	</div><!-- .author-avatar -->

