				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Too many of my sleepless nights are the product of what my past yoga instructor  called”monkey brain”.  I am often plagued by it. I guess I should just relax and “go with the flow”.<br />
I enjoy receiving your ruminations, and hope that both you and Christina<br />
are well.</p>
