					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://thinkingwithnate.wordpress.com/2022/07/06/mindfulness-and-the-default-mode-network/#comment-62"><time datetime="2022-07-09T21:33:38-07:00">July 9, 2022 at 9:33 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

