				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I feel like the monkeybrain -is- going with the flow!  It&#8217;s the brain taking you where it wants without conscious input, like a river running along its established channels.  Well, I wish I could find a way to sleep when I&#8217;m not sleepy, and being distracted by excitement or nerves is often part of that.</p>
<p id="comment-like-62" data-liked=comment-not-liked class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="https://thinkingwithnate.wordpress.com/2022/07/06/mindfulness-and-the-default-mode-network/?like_comment=62&#038;_wpnonce=4c12d8a12c" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="201189235"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-62" class="comment-like-feedback">Like</span></p>
